{"tid":145823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香薰噴霧機一問","createTime":"2017-03-06T14:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T17:37:44.000Z","uid":15819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"542a126754184b6db69d51d0da3efec2dd47747b","tid":145823,"uid":15819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T14:16:49.000Z","msg":"最近朋友送左部香薰噴霧機比我<br />\n但係佢就無送埋香薰油比我<br />\n我出去睇過啲植物精油要百幾蚊先得10ml<br />\n但係有啲含酒精嘅香薰油三百幾就有200ml<br />\n我想問如果我照樣放啲含酒精嘅香薰油落去會唔會出事？<br />\n同埋如果有巴絲都用緊香薰噴霧機嘅<br />\n又可唔可以推薦下用邊隻香薰油性價比會高啲？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4dc0acfa20213a37bfcebd8330f9390b1b64b2","tid":145823,"uid":15819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T14:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f5470863b69e3a8536855b82ee826b0a15a596","tid":145823,"uid":15819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5888a7feb37f93334ac38ec58591cb38abe41400","tid":145823,"uid":15819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbfc16168a61cb58d8e6f49c0eeded65c4948ab9","tid":145823,"uid":15819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c194a99df881dbf1637fbefda698a3763be26d7f","tid":145823,"uid":51571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無印都有 用水溶既<br />\n<br />\n酒精長期聞無咁好 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/